2026-05-13T03:03:47.2176945Z 219            cannot restore it from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-13T03:03:47.2177742Z 220            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-13T03:03:47.2178749Z 221            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-13T03:03:47.2179464Z 222            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-13T03:03:47.2180170Z 223            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-13T03:03:47.2180991Z 224            ensures the activity is finished as soon as it leaves the
2026-05-13T03:03:47.2181791Z 225            foreground and is never re-entered with a missing extra. See
2026-05-13T03:03:47.2182616Z 226            crash report tagged "ProxyBillingActivity NPE" for context.
